rows.label: qst105704_msg0003
rows.name: I have heard, mo. I know...mo!

rows.label: qst105704_msg0005
rows.name:
The head of Lindwurm, the organization
that supported the Avaritia Trade
Guild from the shadows!

rows.label: qst105704_msg0006
rows.name:
Mohhahahahaha! That is good, mo!
For I have been hiding, mo!

rows.label: qst105704_msg0007
rows.name:
It was my creed not to appear in
the open society, but...mo...

rows.label: qst105704_msg0008
rows.name:
...with my son... Bahn,
captured by the Empire, I can
no longer remain silent, mo.

rows.label: qst105704_msg0009
rows.name:
After crushing Superbia, then
Invidia... and then Gula...mo...

rows.label: qst105704_msg0010
rows.name:
...and finally, I was planning
to hunt you all down, mo.

rows.label: qst105704_msg0011
rows.name:
Change of plans, mo! I will
show you something wonderful
on the surface, mo!
